@baseUrl = http://localhost:7080/nyc

# Tile coordinates used below are for central NYC (approx. 40.71°N, 74.01°W)
# WebMercatorQuad:  z=10 → 10/384/301   z=12 → 12/1538/1206   z=14 → 14/6155/4826

### Available tiling schemes (dataset level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiling-schemes?f=json

###

### Dataset tile matrix sets (which tiling schemes are enabled)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiles?f=json

###

### Dataset multi-collection tile — zoom 10 (all collections)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/10/384/301?f=mvt

###

### Dataset multi-collection tile — zoom 12
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

###

# --- Per-collection tiles ---

### Subway stations — tile matrix sets
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_subway_stations/tiles?f=json

###

### Subway stations — tile z=12 (point data, fast)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_subway_stations/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

###

### Subway stations — tile z=14 (street level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_subway_stations/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/14/6155/4826?f=mvt

###

### Neighborhoods — tile z=10
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/10/384/301?f=mvt

###

### Neighborhoods — tile z=12
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

###

### Streets — tile z=12
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_streets/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

###

### Streets — tile z=14 (most detail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_streets/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/14/6155/4826?f=mvt

###

### Census blocks — tile z=12
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_census_blocks/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

###

### Homicides — tile z=12
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_homicides/tiles/WebMercatorQuad/12/1538/1206?f=mvt

